narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would say it's a fun class, but not one that you will necessarily come away from feeling like you've learned a large body of knowledge. It's enjoyable though because you get to dance. Thinking and theorizing are fun, but I didn't feel that I gained anything particularly concrete.
Yes, this is an amazing course I seriously recommend it

I would recommend this course. Don't feel like you have to have rhythm or be a dancer - your dance skills are not being graded here. It's really about the research and the understanding of the context behind the dances.
